@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rhadfn(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.36
    v1 = 0.20
    v2 = (wp.sin(v1) + wp.sin((v1 + 0.98 - v1 + 0.56)))
    tmp = wp.cos(v2)
    tmp = ((0.03 / wp.cos(tmp + 0.67)) - v1)
    tmp = 0.57
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.sin(wp.exp(tmp + 0.28)))
    data[tid] = v0
